Name: SUPPLY SHIP STATION NUMBER
Explanation: SUPPLY SHIP STATION DESIGNATOR (NUMBER) PHONETICALLY SPELLED.

Name: AUTHENTICATION POLICY IN PHONETIC ALPHABETICS
Explanation: A PHONETIC ALPHABETIC USED TO IDENTIFY THE AUTHENTICATION.

Name: PHONETIC NUMERIC IDENTIFIER ONE TO NINE
LINE IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE ALPHABETIC PHONETIC IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED TO A LINE IN AN ANTI-JAM COMPLAN.

Name: STATION NUMBER, ALPHABETIC
Explanation: THE NUMERAL DESIGNATOR OF THE CUSTOMER SHIP REPLENISHMENT TRANSFER STATION WHERE THE SPECIFIED CARGO IS REQUIRED.

Name: COLUMN IDENTIFIER, OLD
Explanation: THE CURRENT COLUMN IDENTIFIER IN THE ANTIJAM PLAN, FOR EXAMPLE: "EIGHT".

Name: COLUMN IDENTIFIER, NEW
Explanation: THE NEW COLUMN IDENTIFIER FOR THE ANTIJAM PLAN FOR EXAMPLE: "THREE".
